            "id": "4449242",
            "title": "Horizon Technology Finance announces CEO transition plan",
            "description": "<html><body><div><ul>\n<li>Horizon Technology Finance (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HRZN\" title=\"Horizon Technology Finance\">HRZN</a></span>) announced that, as part of HRZN’s succession planning, Robert D. Pomeroy, Jr. will retire as chief executive officer of the company.</li>\n<li>Gerald A. Michaud will retire as president, both effective June 5, 2025.</li>\n<li>Board has appointed Michael P. Balkin to succeed Pomeroy as CEO. </li>\n<li>Pomeroy will remain chairman of the board after his retirement.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20106746-horizon-technology-finance-names-michael-p-balkin-as-chief-executive-officer\">Press release</a>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</body></html>",
