            "id": "4449232",
            "title": "MDU Resources Group appoints new board chair",
            "description": "<html><body><div><ul>\n<li>MDU Resources Group (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MDU\" title=\"MDU Resources Group, Inc.\">MDU</a></span>) has elected Darrel T. Anderson as its new independent chair of the board, succeeding Dennis W. Johnson, effective immediately.</li>\n<li>Johnson will remain on the board as a director and will continue to serve as chair of the Nominating and Governance committee.</li>\n<li>Anderson joined the board in 2023, and previously served as board vice chair and chair of the Compensation and Human Capital committee.  </li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20106776-mdu-resources-announces-board-leadership-transition-with-new-chair-of-the-board\">Press release</a>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</body></html>",
